---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import FAQSection from '@/components/sections/FAQSection.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="ID and Passport Extraction"
  description="Extract passport and ID card data instantly with OCR — name, DOB, document number, expiry, MRZ. Used for KYC, AML, and onboarding workflows. Free trial."
  canonicalUrl="https://www.formx.ai/tools/id-and-passport-extraction"
>
  <section class="title-2 bg-f7f8fc">
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer pagetitle__container mt-60 w-container">
      <h1 class="pricing-title mb-0">
        <span class="heading-gradient">Passport OCR Trial for&#x2028;<br /></span>Effortless ID Extraction
      </h1>
      <p class="section__header__content mb-40">
        Experience the future of document processing with our <span class="font-weight-700">free Passport OCR trial.</span> &#x2028;Effortlessly extract data from your passports and other IDs with industry-leading accuracy.
      </p>
      <div class="w-embed w-iframe">
        <iframe src="https://widgets.formx.ai/id-card-passport/" style="width: 100%; height: 600px" frameBorder="0"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section product-section bg-f7f8fc">
    <div class="container-default w-container">
      <div class="product-2-block-wrapper m-reverse">
        <div class="product-2-block-text-wrapper">
          <img src="/images/pages/converter_privacy.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" />
          <h2 class="product-2-block-heading">Your Data.<br />Your Privacy.<br />Our Promise.</h2>
          <div class="product-2-block-paragraph">We prioritize user privacy and delete your data after processing with ID Card and Passport OCR.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-2-block-image-wrapper">
          <img
            src="/images/pages/converter_medical_ocr_compliance@2x.webp"
            loading="lazy"
            width="600"
            sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 600px"
            alt=""
            srcset="/images/pages/converter_medical_ocr_compliance@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_medical_ocr_compliance@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_medical_ocr_compliance@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/converter_medical_ocr_compliance@2x.webp 1248w"
            class="image-rounded"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="container-default heading-content w-container">
      <div class="product-heading-wrapper mx-auto mb-60 max-width-800">
        <h2 class="product-heading">What is Passport OCR?&#x2028;<br /><span class="heading-gradient">Unlocking the Power of Passport OCR</span></h2>
        <div class="product-subheading">OCR technology offers a plethora of applications within the insurance industry. Here are some key use cases:</div>
      </div>

      <div class="product-2-block-wrapper mb-60 reverse">
        <div class="product-2-block-text-wrapper gap-0">
          <h2 class="product-2-block-heading">Government Agencies</h2>
          <div class="gradient-divider"></div>
          <ul role="list" class="_2-block-flex-content-list">
            <li class="_2-block-flex-content-list-item check-4pxtop"><div class="_2-block-flex-content-text-wrap">Immigration Checks</div></li>
            <li class="_2-block-flex-content-list-item check-4pxtop"><div class="_2-block-flex-content-text-wrap">Border Control</div></li>
            <li class="_2-block-flex-content-list-item check-4pxtop"><div class="_2-block-flex-content-text-wrap">Voter registration</div></li>
            <li class="_2-block-flex-content-list-item check-4pxtop"><div class="_2-block-flex-content-text-wrap">Driver's license issuance</div></li>
            <li class="_2-block-flex-content-list-item check-4pxtop"><div class="_2-block-flex-content-text-wrap">Law enforcement investigations</div></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="product-2-block-image-wrapper">
          <img
            src="/images/pages/converter_id_whatis-government@2x.webp"
            loading="lazy"
            width="600"
            sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 600px"
            alt=""
            srcset="/images/pages/converter_id_whatis-government@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_id_whatis-government@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_id_whatis-government@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/converter_id_whatis-government@2x.webp 1248w"
            class="image-rounded"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="product-2-block-wrapper mb-60 m-reverse">
        <div class="product-2-block-text-wrapper gap-0">
          <h2 class="product-2-block-heading">Financial Institutions</h2>
          <div class="gradient-divider"></div>
          <ul role="list" class="_2-block-flex-content-list">
            <li class="_2-block-flex-content-list-item check-4pxtop"><div class="_2-block-flex-content-text-wrap">Customer onboarding</div></li>
            <li class="_2-block-flex-content-list-item check-4pxtop"><div class="_2-block-flex-content-text-wrap">Anti-money laundering (AML) compliance</div></li>
            <li class="_2-block-flex-content-list-item check-4pxtop"><div class="_2-block-flex-content-text-wrap">Know Your Customer (KYC) verification</div></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="product-2-block-image-wrapper">
          <img
            src="/images/pages/converter_id_whatis-financial@2x.webp"
            loading="lazy"
            width="600"
            sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 600px"
            alt=""
            srcset="/images/pages/converter_id_whatis-financial@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_id_whatis-financial@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_id_whatis-financial@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/converter_id_whatis-financial@2x.webp 1248w"
            class="image-rounded"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="product-2-block-wrapper mb-60 reverse">
        <div class="product-2-block-text-wrapper gap-0">
          <h2 class="product-2-block-heading">Online Businesses</h2>
          <div class="gradient-divider"></div>
          <ul role="list" class="_2-block-flex-content-list">
            <li class="_2-block-flex-content-list-item check-4pxtop"><div class="_2-block-flex-content-text-wrap">Age verification</div></li>
            <li class="_2-block-flex-content-list-item check-4pxtop"><div class="_2-block-flex-content-text-wrap">Identity theft prevention</div></li>
            <li class="_2-block-flex-content-list-item check-4pxtop"><div class="_2-block-flex-content-text-wrap">Account registration</div></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="product-2-block-image-wrapper">
          <img
            src="/images/pages/converter_id_whatis-online@2x.webp"
            loading="lazy"
            width="600"
            sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 600px"
            alt=""
            srcset="/images/pages/converter_id_whatis-online@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_id_whatis-online@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_id_whatis-online@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/converter_id_whatis-online@2x.webp 1248w"
            class="image-rounded"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="product-2-block-wrapper mb-60 m-reverse">
        <div class="product-2-block-text-wrapper gap-0">
          <h2 class="product-2-block-heading">Rental Companies</h2>
          <div class="gradient-divider"></div>
          <ul role="list" class="_2-block-flex-content-list">
            <li class="_2-block-flex-content-list-item check-4pxtop"><div class="_2-block-flex-content-text-wrap">Tenant screening</div></li>
            <li class="_2-block-flex-content-list-item check-4pxtop"><div class="_2-block-flex-content-text-wrap">Background checks</div></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="product-2-block-image-wrapper">
          <img
            src="/images/pages/converter_id_whatis-rental@2x.webp"
            loading="lazy"
            width="600"
            sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 600px"
            alt=""
            srcset="/images/pages/converter_id_whatis-rental@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/converter_id_whatis-rental@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/converter_id_whatis-rental@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/converter_id_whatis-rental@2x.webp 1248w"
            class="image-rounded"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <FAQSection
    heading="Frequently Asked Questions"
    items={[
      {
        question: "What data does FormX extract from a passport or ID card?",
        answer: `FormX extracts full name, date of birth, nationality, document number, issue and expiry dates, issuing authority, and MRZ (machine-readable zone) data. For ID cards, it also extracts address where present. Output is available as JSON or Excel. <a href="/schedule-demo">Get in touch</a> to see a demo.<br />`,
      },
      {
        question: "What document types does the ID extraction tool support?",
        answer: `FormX supports passports, national ID cards, driver's licences, and residence permits from most countries. Documents can be submitted as PDF, JPG, or PNG — including phone photographs. <a href="/schedule-demo">Contact us</a> to verify support for a specific document type.<br />`,
      },
      {
        question: "How does FormX help with KYC and onboarding workflows?",
        answer: `FormX extracts structured identity data from uploaded documents and returns it as JSON, which can be fed directly into KYC platforms, CRM systems, or onboarding workflows via REST API. This removes manual data entry from identity verification steps. <a href="/schedule-demo">Schedule a demo</a> to see the integration.<br />`,
      },
      {
        question: "Is identity document data safe when processed by FormX?",
        answer: `FormX is ISO 27001 and SOC 2 Type II certified. All uploaded documents are encrypted in transit (TLS 1.2+) and at rest (AES-256). Documents are not retained after extraction. Read our <a href="/data-privacy-policy" target="_blank">data privacy policy</a> for more.<br />`,
      },
      {
        question: "Is there a free trial for passport and ID extraction?",
        answer: `Yes — the web tool is free with no signup required for single document extraction. Batch processing and API access require a free trial account. <a href="https://formextractorai.com/signup" target="_blank">Sign up</a> or <a href="/schedule-demo">contact us</a> to get started.<br />`,
      },
    ]}
  />

  <section class="section whats-new">
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-default w-container">
      <div class="whats-new-last-section">
        <div class="whats-new-content-wrap">
          <h2 class="whats-new-last-section-heading color-white">Expanding Your Toolkit: FormX.ai Beyond Passport OCR</h2>
        </div>
        <a href="/schedule-demo" class="button-primary button-white w-button">Schedule a Demo -&gt;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
